              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/status/200:0.7,500:0.3",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["status", "200:0.7,500:0.3"]
            },
            "description": "Returns a random status code from the provided list with optional weights.\n\nFormat: `code1:weight1,code2:weight2,...`\n\nExample: `200:0.7,500:0.3` returns 200 (70% chance) or 500 (30% chance).\n\nIf no weights are provided (e.g., `200,404,500`), each code has equal probability."
